			<p>Oil production from countries outside the <a href="/tools/glossary/index.php?id=O#opec">Organization of the Petroleum Exporting Countries (OPEC)</a> currently represents about 60 percent of world oil production. Key centers of non-OPEC production include North America, regions of the former Soviet Union, and the North Sea.</p>
